Troubleshooting Tips
Issue: JADX decompilation fails

Solution: Try jadx --show-bad-code -d output malicious_sample.apk to force decompilation of problematic code
Issue: No strings extracted from DEX files

Solution: Verify DEX files extracted correctly with file dex_files/*.dex and ensure strings utility is installed
Issue: Python script import errors

Solution: Install required libraries: pip3 install requests
Issue: Cannot find C2 addresses in code

Solution: Check for dynamic string construction, look in configuration classes, and examine network-related imports
